In Acumatica ERP, you can maintain all the necessary information about equipment that your company uses to perform services. You can enter the equipment information, such as its serial number, registration information, manufacturing information, purchase information, owner, and location. With this information in the system, users can quickly search for the necessary equipment in the system. {br}
This chapter describes how to manage equipment that is used to perform services that your staff members deliver. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_d8179654-cce4-440f-b8a1-a945d89be39c] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#_e4517db2-6269-4344-9a83-8058786d46f1] *[HelpRoot_FieldServices\FS__CON_Resource_Equipment|Resource Equipment]
